Film Summaries

NEW YORK
Lucky Number Slevin 18
A case of mistaken identity lands Slevin into the middle of a war between two of the city's top crime bosses, The Rabbi and The Boss.
Starring Josh Hartnett, Bruce Willis, Lucy Liu, Morgan Freeman and Sir Ben Kingsley.
Crime, Drama, Mystery, Thriller
language: english
UK release: 7 April 2006

PACIFIC OCEAN
Life of Pi PG
A young man survives a shipwreckat sea and is hurtled into an epic journey of adventure and discovery, forming an unexpected journey with Richard Parker, a fearsome Bengal tiger.
Starring Suraj Sharma and Irrfan Khan
Directed by Ang Lee
Adventure, Drama, Fantasy
language: English, Tamil, French, Japanese, Hindi, Chinese
21 November 2012

LONDON
About a Boy 12
A cynical, immature young man is taught how to act like a grown up by a little boy.
Starring Hugh Grant, Nicholas Hoult and Toni Collette
Comedy, Drama, Romance
language: English
26 April 2002

SEOUL
200 Pound Beauty
Han-na, a talented but overweight girl who provides the vocals for a not so talented pop star, makes a big decision in order to achieve her dreams.
Starring Jim-mo Ju, Ah Jung Kim and Dong-il Sung
Comedy, Drama, Music, Romance
language: Korean
14 Decemeber 2006

TAIWAN
Hear Me
A delivery boy falls in love with a hearing impaired young girl; together they try to break the barriers facing them and pursue their dreams.
Starring Eddie Peng, Ivy Yi-Han Chen and Michelle Chen
Drama, Romance
language: Sign Language, Chinese
28 Aug 2009

MITTE, BERLIN
Run Lola Run/ Lola Rennt 15
After her boyfriend botches fails to deliver money to the wrong kind of people, Lola has 20 minutes to come up with 100,000 Deutschmarks.
Starring Franka Potente, Moritz Bliebtreu and Herbert Knaup
Crime, Drama, Thriller
language:German, English, Japanese
22 October 1999

BERLIN
The Wave/ Das Welle 15
A high school teacher's experiment on life under a dictatorship spins horribly out of control.
Starring Fredrick Lau, Max Riemelt and Jennifer Ulrich
Drama, Thriller
language: German
19 September 2008

SIERRA LEONE
Blood Diamond 15
A fisherman, a smuggler and a syndicate of businessmen match wits over the possesion of a priceless diamond.
Starring Leonardo DiCaprio, Djimon Hounsou and Jennifer Connelly
Adventure, Drama, Thriller
language: English, Mende, Afrikaans
26 January 2007

